<div class="container my-5">
  <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

  <dl>
    <dt>How do I book a house on StayNook?</dt>
    <dd>Search for your destination, choose a listing, and follow the secure checkout process.</dd>

    <dt>Can I cancel or change my booking?</dt>
    <dd>Yes, cancellation and modification options are available based on the host's policy.</dd>

    <dt>What payment methods are accepted?</dt>
    <dd>We accept all major credit/debit cards and selected digital wallets.</dd>

    <dt>How do I contact a host?</dt>
    <dd>Use the in-app messaging feature after a booking is confirmed.</dd>
  </dl>
</div>
